  "texts": [
    "For example, standardized formats and units allow for easier comparisons and trend analysis, ensuring consistency in the data [191,192].",
    "(3) Enhanced decision-making: Clean and preprocessed data supports better decision-making by providing accurate and actionable insights.",
    "Food systems professionals rely on these insights to make important decisions regarding product recalls, regulatory compliance, and improvements in food production and storage processes.",
    "Without proper data cleaning and preprocessing, decisions could be based on faulty or incomplete data, leading to inefficient outcomes [193,194].",
    "(4) Efficient data integration: Preprocessed and cleaned data can be easily integrated from multiple sources, such as sensors, imaging systems, and textual reports."
